extends baseEmail

block content
    div(style="padding: 60px 30px 40px 30px; border: 1px solid #ccd1d6; border-radius: 8px; font-family: sans-serif;")
        h2(style="margin-bottom: 20px; font-size: 20px; color: #333;") Confirm Your Email Change Request
        p(style="font-size: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; color: #444;") Hello #{firstName},
        p(style="font-size: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; color: #444;") We received a request to change the email address associated with your Auth API account.
        p(style="font-size: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; color: #444;") To confirm this change, please click the button below within the next 15 minutes:

        div(style="margin: 24px 0;")
            a(
                href=`${payload}`, target='_blank',
                style="display: inline-block; padding: 12px 20px; background-color: #080a0bde; color: #fff; border-radius: 5px; text-decoration: none; font-weight: 600; font-size: 14px; text-align: center;"
            ) Confirm Email Change

        p(style="font-size: 14px; margin-top: 24px; margin-bottom: 8px; color: #666;")
            | If the button above doesn't work, copy and paste the URL below into your browser:
        p(style="word-break: break-word; font-size: 14px; margin-bottom: 24px;")
            a(href=`${payload}`, target='_blank' style="color: #006ed1; text-decoration: underline;") #{payload}

        p(style="font-size: 14px; color: #999;")
            | If you did not request this change, you can safely ignore this message.

